## §4 Execution sequence

team_110 executes in order:
1. Implement all ACs per spec
2. Route L-GATE_BUILD mandate → team_90 (`_COMMUNICATION/team_90/MANDATE_{WP_ID}_L-GATE_BUILD_v1.0.0.md`)
3. On team_90 PASS/PASS_WITH_FINDINGS: route L-GATE_VALIDATE mandate → team_190
4. On team_190 PASS/PASS_WITH_FINDINGS: execute ADR042 3-step closure
   - Step 1: Write `_archive/{WP_ID}/ARCHIVE_MANIFEST.md`
   - Step 2: `POST /api/work-packages/{WP_ID}` → `status: COMPLETE, lod_status: LOD500_LOCKED`
     (or file-canonical per ADR034 R10 if hub-native WP)
   - Step 3: If `core/governance/` modified → `bash scripts/aos_sync_all.sh --all`
5. File COMPLETION_REPORT → `_COMMUNICATION/team_110/{WP_ID}/COMPLETION_REPORT_{WP_ID}_v1.0.0.md`

