## §5 Completion criteria

WP is complete when:
- [ ] All ACs verified
- [ ] team_90 L-GATE_BUILD: PASS or PASS_WITH_FINDINGS (0 blockers)
- [ ] team_190 L-GATE_VALIDATE: PASS or PASS_WITH_FINDINGS (0 blockers)
- [ ] `_archive/{WP_ID}/ARCHIVE_MANIFEST.md` exists
- [ ] `metadata.yaml` → `status: COMPLETE, lod_status: LOD500_LOCKED`
- [ ] `_aos/roadmap.yaml` WP entry updated (closed_at, COMPLETE status)
- [ ] `validate_aos.sh` Check 32 PASS
- [ ] COMPLETION_REPORT filed to team_00 + team_100
- [ ] Merged to main + pushed to origin

